{"tid":25901,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［問全能既連登仔］有冇人知呢隻咩黎？","createTime":"2016-12-06T11:45:49.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T11:58:29.000Z","uid":32879,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b681c9f0567e1464f16d4d5fe5b5bbf8708c8acb","tid":25901,"uid":32879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/899iMEw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F899iMEw.jpg&h=b610ff64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前間中先會見到一兩隻<br />\n今日一入廚房就見到連續幾隻係啲碗碟到爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗諗下呢排就連廳都見到<br />\n屋企又唔係話污糟左好多 啲碗碟檢查過又洗得乾淨<br />\n有冇人知咩黎？<br />\n點知可以減少佢地<br />\n爬完係啲碗碟又要再洗過好煩<br />\n<br />\n利申：成隻甲蟲仔咁覺得佢好可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5b18bcb856d01756d3993375be5b2f5fa1dbdd","tid":25901,"uid":32879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:53:32.000Z","msg":"求教"},{"pid":"6c6e3409a4d88c7ba2fba830c9e5c7fd265b30b6","tid":25901,"uid":12579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"唔知"},{"pid":"57bdea7573eac1de80bcd8aed557e4eec7370273","tid":25901,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:55:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b46bf4dbb10c3dabf26e7d91c8d64689a15f828b","tid":25901,"uid":43244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:55:33.000Z","msg":"微波爐適用白玉瓷"},{"pid":"c377c1fcf53559f7d2ea2cb5c8f67304bbea6f8d","tid":25901,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:56:51.000Z","msg":"你放返入米缸養"},{"pid":"e4fff9d552c50dd93c61f1d0ffd228c5157885af","tid":25901,"uid":32879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T11:57:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>穀蟲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n真係全能架<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/